Package: nof1
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of N of 1 Trials
Version: 0.5.0
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: rjags (>= 4-6), splines, combinat, MASS, jsonlite, ggplot2, scales, coda (>= 0.13)
Authors@R: c( 
	person("Michael", "Seo", email = "michael_seo@brown.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	person("Christopher", "Schmid", email = "christopher_schmid@brown.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: A package for running analysis for N of 1 study trials. Runs Bayesian linear regression, ordinal/logistic regression, and poisson regression. Includes different plots to visualize the results.
